[2] Saudi Arabia MOH 6-9 Aug 2019
Date: Fri 9 Aug 2019
Source: Saudi MOH 6-9 Aug 2019 [edited]
https://www.moh.gov.sa/en/CCC/events/national/Pages/2019.aspx


In the 4 days since the last update [MERS-CoV (59): Saudi Arabia (RI, QS) 20190805.6607355], there have been no newly confirmed cases of MERS-CoV infection reported by Saudi Arabia. In addition, there have been no new reports of outcomes of the 2 previously reported cases currently listed as active cases.

